e>\n<caption>标题</caption>\n    <thead>\n        <th>行标题1</th>\n        <th>行标题2</th>\n    </thead>\n<tbody>\n    <tr>\n        <td>项目1</td>\n        <td>项目2</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td></td>\n        <td></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td></td>\n        <td></td>\n    </tr>\n</tbody>\n<tfoot>\n    <tr>\n        <td></td>\n        <td></td>\n    </tr>\n</tfoot>\n</table>\n```\n\n`colspan`：跨列合并<br>\n`rowspan`：跨行合并\n\n\n## 表单\n\n::: info Emmet 语法\n`form`\n:::\n\n> [!important]\n>\n> [表单练习](/article/glcwr3r6/)\n\n```html\n<form action=\"\">\n</form>\n```\n\n### input\n\n| Type     | 说明     | 属性                       | Emment语法 | 图片                                        |\n| -------- | -------- | -------------------------- | ---------- | ------------------------------------------- |\n| text     | 文本框   | placeholder、width、height | `input:t`  | ![](/html/image_1690643854165.png)          |\n| password | 密码     | name、placeholder          | `input:p`  | ![](/html/image_1690643510012.png)          |\n| radio    | 单选框   | name、checked              | `input:r`  | ![](/html/Snipaste_2023-07-29_23-09-15.png) |\n| checkbox | 多选框   | name、checked              | `input:c`  | ![](/html/image_1690643076762.png)          |\n| file     | 文件选择 | value                      | `input:f`  | ![](/html/image_1690643203381.png)          |\n| submit   | 提交     | value                      | `input:s`  | ![](/html/image_1690643266296.png)          |\n| reset    | 重置     | value                      |            |                                             |\n| button   | 普通     | value                      | `input:b`  | ![](/html/image_1690642716649.png)          |\n\n::: warning\n\n通常不会使用button属性\n:::\n\n\n- `placeholder`    提示文字\n- `checked`    默认状态\n- `value`    可修改按钮名称\n\n### button\n\n| Type   | 说明 | 属性  |\n| ------ | ---- | ----- |\n| submit | 提交 | value |\n| reset  | 重置 | value |\n\n### select\n\n::: info Emmet 语法\n`select>option*2`\n:::\n\n::: normal-demo\n\n```html\n<select>\n    <option>red</option>\n    <option selected>blue</option>\n</select>\n```\n\n:::\n\n### textarea\n\n::: info Emmet 语法\n`textarea`\n:::\n\n```html\n<textarea></textarea>\n```\n\n`cols`：可见宽度<br>\n`rows`：可见行数\n\n### label\n\n::: normal-demo\n\n```html\n性别<input type=\"radio\" name=\"sex\" id=\"nan\"> <label for=\"nan\">男</label>\n<label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"sex\"> 女</label>\n```\n\n:::\n\n### blockquote\n\n<blockquote>\n    内容\n</blockquote>\n\n## 无语义标签\n\n- div\n- span\n\n## 有语义标签\n\n```html\n<header>网页头部</header>\n<nav>网页导航</nav>\n<footer>网页底部</footer>\n<aside>侧边栏</aside>\n<section>网页区块</section>\n<article>文章</article>\n```\n\n## 字符实体\n\n```html\n <!-- 网页不认识多个空格, 只认识一个 -->\n这是HTML文档, 现在要学&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;习字符实体.\n```","excerpt":"","tasklists":0,"title":"","headers":[{"level":2,"title":"列表","slug":"列表","link":"#列表","children":[{"level":3,"title":"无序","slug":"无序","link":"#无序","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"有序","slug":"有序","link":"#有序","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"自定义","slug":"自定义","link":"#自定义","children":[]}]},{"level":2,"title":"表格","slug":"表格","link":"#表格","children":[]},{"level":2,"title":"表单","slug":"表单","link":"#表单","children":[{"level":3,"title":"input","slug":"input","link":"#input","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"button","slug":"button","link":"#button","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"select","slug":"select","link":"#select","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"textarea","slug":"textarea","link":"#textarea","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"label","slug":"label","link":"#label","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"blockquote","slug":"blockquote","link":"#blockquote","children":[]}]},{"level":2,"title":"无语义标签","slug":"无语义标签","link":"#无语义标签","children":[]},{"level":2,"title":"有语义标签","slug":"有语义标签","link":"#有语义标签","children":[]},{"level":2,"title":"字符实体","slug":"字符实体","link":"#字符实体","children":[]}],"links":[{"raw":"/article/glcwr3r6/","relative":"article/glcwr3r6","absolute":"/article/glcwr3r6/